Package: CalciumInsights
Title: Interactive Analysis of Calcium-Imaging Time Series
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Deiver",
      family = "Suarez",
      email = "deiver.suarez@upr.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: A modular Shiny application for interactive post-processing,
    visualization, event detection, baseline sensitivity analysis, and
    quantification of calcium-imaging time-series data. The active workflows
    provide FFT-based denoising and baseline analysis and wavelet-based
    ridgewalking event detection.
